00:00:09.569 --> 00:00:12.504
- [Narrator] We are the paradoxical eight.

00:00:12.504 --> 00:00:15.004
Bipedal, naked, large-brained.

00:00:17.633 --> 00:00:21.756
Long the master of fire,
tools and language.

00:00:21.756 --> 00:00:25.987
But still trying to understand ourselves.

00:00:25.987 --> 00:00:29.102
Aware that death is inevitable,

00:00:29.102 --> 00:00:31.185
yet filled with optimism.

00:00:32.563 --> 00:00:34.063
We grow up slowly.

00:00:34.977 --> 00:00:37.611
We hand down knowledge.

00:00:37.611 --> 00:00:39.694
We empathize and deceive.

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:42.187
We shape the future

00:00:42.187 --> 00:00:46.515
from our shared understanding of the past.

00:00:46.515 --> 00:00:48.563
Carta brings together experts

00:00:48.563 --> 00:00:50.326
from diverse disciplines

00:00:50.326 --> 00:00:53.363
to exchange insights on who we are

00:00:53.363 --> 00:00:55.030
and how we got here,

00:00:56.491 --> 00:00:58.163
an exploration made possible

00:00:58.163 --> 00:01:01.246
by the generosity of humans like you.

00:01:22.138 --> 00:01:24.721
(lively music)

00:01:27.716 --> 00:01:30.299
